{"type": "article", "id": 45595, "title": "Nike 利润大跌，以及，adidas 高管涉嫌篮球腐败案被捕 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-09-27T03:21:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 44374, "name": "FENDI"}, {"id": 3133, "name": "Jil Sander"}, {"id": 17255, "name": "KITH"}, {"id": 44341, "name": "colette"}, {"id": 37120, "name": "Acne Studio"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 44375, "name": "coty"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170927103548MnlU9ZtjxI1SoasP.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-4923372/Nike-profits-drop-North-American-weakness.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>受北美地区大规模促销影响，Nike 利润下滑 </strong></a>| 周二，Nike 公布了最新的季度财报。报道显示，截止至 8 月 31 日的这一季度，Nike 集团销售额与去年持平，为 91 亿美元，但净利润大跌 24％ 至 9.5 亿美元。Nike 在北美以外的地区均获得了增长，但受北美地区大规模促销及汇率影响，削减了利润。 </p><p><a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/mikeozanian/2017/09/26/shares-of-adidas-hammered-by-college-bribery-scandal/#6f7bca5c3ecb\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>adidas 全球营销总监 Jim Gatto 涉嫌篮球腐败案被捕</strong></a> | 美国联邦检察机关提起诉讼，称美国部分顶尖大学篮球项目的教练受贿。该案件涉及 10 名相关人士，包括大学教练、经理、金融顾问和体育服装公司。adidas 的全球营销总监 Jim Gatto 被指控称，贿赂高中篮球运动员和其家人，诱导他们加入与 adidas 有合作关系的大学球队，然后在转向职业运动员时与 adidas 签约。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/mergers-acquisitions/beyonce-vera-wang-jovan-fragrances-said-to-be-on-coty-divestment-agenda-11000800/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Coty 将出售部分名人香水代理权</strong></a> | 据 wwd 消息，Coty 将出售旗下 10 个品牌香水的代理权，包括 David Beckham、Beyoncé 和 Jennifer Lopez 等名人香水品牌，其中 Jennifer Lopez 香水已确认将出售给 Designer Parfums，其余品牌正在等待投标，截止日期为 10 月中旬。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>做形似香烟的糖出名的大阪品牌 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/fr2-collaborate-with-japanese-old-dagashi-orions-cocoa-cigarette\" rel=\"nofollow\">ORION’S</a>，联合日本街头品牌，推出一款以 Fxxking Rabbits 为元素包装的香烟状巧克力，在日本元素的 FR2 门店发售，定价 100 日元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105501tvs91Y3o0ZcD8SzX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709271055019bK1okMnN7rysIpC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105508cO14aoPlVn3HszrJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Acne Studio 推出了最新球鞋 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/dad-sneakers-acne-studios-sofiane-sneakers\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sofiane Sneakers</a>。这双鞋采用了今年大热的 Dad Shoes 老爸鞋的设计，搭配薄荷绿配色..嗯，看起来丑丑的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709271055443aX6GILhFW7uDt1e.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709271055511EypQmuik2ahxB69.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>利用近场磁感应技术（NFMI）连结左右声道，瑞典品牌 YEVO Labs 制作出了真正的无线耳机，它的设计更轻巧，且连线距离长达 10 米。 </p><p>9 月 26 日，<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/yevo-colette-limited-edition-true-wireless-headphones\" rel=\"nofollow\">YEVO 联合 colette </a>推出了限定色无线耳机，售价 249 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105607y0Z8BYqU4OQVEL6T.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666097\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105608UNIdwoXR4hLvYt0Z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709271056091vxfoDTAnyCVGYrU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>KITH 和 Nike 合作的&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/09/27/kith-nike-lookbook/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Take Flight </a>系列，目前已发布官方 lookbook。 </p><p>该系列的灵感来自 KITH 创始人 Ronnie Fieg 童年时代的偶像、球员 Scottie Pippen，包括球衣、运动鞋等多款单品，将于 9 月 29 日率先发售。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105653mlywOkiqZfA9nRL6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105652tmRIPWN32CGzY1FD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105649g7sLtKAFCfXi9uqy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105652Dvu8PfLRMmjH1gZo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105653Jgt3HpULjlQbZAIM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105656oTpYCrkjgdzuLlF7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105656W1myoetRlw0pnQkZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105657ILFNbp6f2sgyTrjE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105658c1wQs3meatkqv4J9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105658UyQWCGwaXPvoVf7g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105659ibZ0dU1VhRQPO5Gq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105659lr1SXEVcAhWoQTMG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>米兰时装周，换了新 logo 的<a href=\"https://popbee.com/accessories/handbags/new-logo-fendi-bag-2018ss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Fendi </a>第二次登场。2018 春夏系列新品手袋以格纹和花卉图案为主，色调柔和。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105734WdHGZ92CgchBiueJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105737r9cv4B68syCael5j.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709271057379XeRUuwZKf8qIc3S.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105738fUoBKd0WZDR3T48c.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105739hgzr8pA71mdLPRko.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105739l40Yh9AJyp7zrXdn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105739tWGrwIsBMFNHY0gT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105741muzXGgOjnH1vPpeY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105742L6R8cn3y9qavUDCe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105743RFzwryUNPV29EOG3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105743eIta64dEfwiOqXRP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105744ijfrxJmhkEecRCNG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105743tpvcseITnBfJ9D7d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105744nJtzDVRYbKvuc4AO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105745irAo6GUjQVHyPDNb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105745BqxyaLHQ3Y2bAw1M.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105746V4zoMZJXmjL92DW5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://popbee.com/fashion/runway-fashion/jil-sander-ss2018-milan-fashion-week/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jil Sander</a> 在扎哈设计的 CityLife 走了一场秀。这一季的新品延续了设计师夫妇 Lucie Meier &amp; Luke 的经典款白衬衫，另外加入了百褶、泡泡袖、不规则剪裁等细节。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105829K9C2gDsBqOA6Xuta.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105829is0wzTHLCQIDepXF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105829t5EFnNw6pZ42xkgf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105829s18QJPTi2Ezba7Lr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105829WLy8FtCo7GPfdOYE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105830IN5XdZCjfF8EYuxB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105830GIJBCWTDL4ePVUAl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170927105832VxMYK7W84vNzL2ae.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2